# Cross-origin isolation → the viewer's compute runs off the main thread (SharedArrayBuffer/worker) instead of
# freezing the UI. COOP+COEP turn isolation on; CORP on every response keeps same-origin subresources embeddable.
# (Tracked here so `server/deploy.sh` ships it — otherwise rsync --delete would prune the server-only copy.)
Header always set Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy "same-origin"
Header always set Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy "require-corp"
Header always set Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy "cross-origin"
